Skewer - retired blade technique name
------------------------------------------------------------
Skewer was the former name for the Impale blade technique.
Use 'starttech impale' to concentrate on deep piercing
strikes. Impale's damage now increases at each character-
level bracket: +45 below Hero, +56 at Hero, +67 at Legend,
+78 at Epic, and +90 at Mythic.

GL: 11
SP:  9 / proc, reduced by Flow
command:  starttech impale
duration: technique mode
